## Order check
- [ ] Question-first opening (not "the goal of this project was…")
- [ ] First result appears before the midpoint
- [ ] Dives ordered by logical dependency, not chronology
- [ ] Closes on implications of the core message, not "Future Directions"
- [ ] Every Build-list prerequisite has a home in the stepping-stones table
- [ ] No dive contains two sub-questions or two results (split if so)
